Our food is carefully created using the freshest ingredients made from scratch. There are two cardinal rules of Italian cuisine – eat locally and eat seasonally. We would like to introduce you to Cafe Murano’s in house Catering Service. We can provide anything and everything you need for your next event.
Catering is not just about great food and great service, It’s all about all those little things we make look so easy.
At Cafe Murano we cater to a wide variety of clientele with very different taste in food, styles and budgets. We specialize in Weddings, Rehearsal Dinners, Bridal Luncheons, and Baby Showers.
We have the staff, the Expertise and Experience to create and execute any style event our client (you) would like.
